abstract: A black teenager’s murder conviction, handled by Ms. Klobuchar’s office, was “one of the most flawed investigations and prosecutions that I think I have ever seen,” said Sunny Hostin, a co-host who is herself a former prosecutor.
snippet: A black teenager’s murder conviction, handled by Ms. Klobuchar’s office, was “one of the most flawed investigations and prosecutions that I think I have ever seen,” said Sunny Hostin, a co-host who is herself a former prosecutor.
lead_paragraph: MANCHESTER, N.H. — Senator Amy Klobuchar of Minnesota faced tough questions from a host of “The View,” Sunny Hostin, during an interview on Tuesday regarding her handling of the conviction of a black teenager when she was a county prosecutor.

abstract: Seeking a revival, Ms. Warren’s campaign manager sent a letter to supporters expressing optimism about her path forward while taking a skeptical view of her leading opponents.
snippet: Seeking a revival, Ms. Warren’s campaign manager sent a letter to supporters expressing optimism about her path forward while taking a skeptical view of her leading opponents.
lead_paragraph: MANCHESTER, N.H. — In a lengthy Election Day memo outlining their path forward in the fractured Democratic primary, Elizabeth Warren’s campaign manager drew the sharpest contrasts to date with her leading rivals, arguing that Bernie Sanders has a political “ceiling,” Joseph R. Biden Jr. is at risk of having his support collapse and that Pete Buttigieg will struggle as the primary moves on to more diverse states.

abstract: Days before the Iowa caucuses, Democratic Party activist Lindsey Ellickson prepared to run her Cedar Rapids precinct by downloading the new smartphone app designed to calculate and report results.
snippet: Days before the Iowa caucuses, Democratic Party activist Lindsey Ellickson prepared to run her Cedar Rapids precinct by downloading the new smartphone app designed to calculate and report results.
lead_paragraph: IOWA CITY, Iowa — Days before the Iowa caucuses, Democratic Party activist Lindsey Ellickson prepared to run her Cedar Rapids precinct by downloading the new smartphone app designed to calculate and report results.
headline_main: How the Iowa Caucuses 'Broke Down in Every Way Possible'
headline_print_headline: How the Iowa Caucuses 'Broke Down in Every Way Possible'

abstract: Volunteers and activists in rural towns and swing counties are demoralized but still vow to turn out in November.
snippet: Volunteers and activists in rural towns and swing counties are demoralized but still vow to turn out in November.
lead_paragraph: DES MOINES — After Iowa’s Democratic caucuses melted down into a long night of technology glitches and error-riddled results, Laura Hubka, the chairwoman of the Howard County Democrats, got up the next morning and faced the aftermath at the grocery store.

lead_paragraph: MANCHESTER, N.H. — Senator Bernie Sanders of Vermont won New Hampshire’s Democratic presidential primary Tuesday night, consolidating support on the left in his second strong showing in as many weeks.
